{"type": "article", "id": 10240, "title": "月亮躺椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-01T07:41:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135130j6aL9E7WRONQhzi2.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是斯洛维尼亚家具品牌 Lina 推出的一个多功能躺椅，这个叫做 “Moon Chaise Lounge”（月亮躺椅）的作品采用模块化的设计，通过不同元素的组合，可以形成桌子，椅子，沙发等，颜色靓丽鲜明。此外，软垫可拆卸、可水洗，不用的时候可以方便地堆在一边塞进角落里面。目前产品售价 176 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.lovethesign.com/uk/lina/moon-chaise-longue\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135128b8K2gI75WN1uCEFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135129wFA8B1Xon7r4QCpz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135129lbKpfJ75TxRz6AaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54767726\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135129gF1lR8OUWMZnpsmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135130nBZr5JzmjdL7OElN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87286064\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}